OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1777486270
OL,3,CRising fuel bills hit lifesaving blood
OL,4,Cbiker service
OL,6,FA charity which delivers urgent blood
OL,7,Fsamples, medication, and other
OL,8,Furgently required medical items is
OL,9,Flooking for more volunteers to help
OL,10,Ffundraise for them, as the cost of
OL,11,Ffuel increases due to the war in Iran.
OL,13,FThe Dumfries and Galloway Blood Bike
OL,14,Fteam says the cost of fuel has
OL,15,Fincreased from around #3,500 pounds a
OL,16,Fmonth, to around #5,000.
OL,18,FThe charity clocks around 18,000 miles
OL,19,Fon the road per month.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
