OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1777486270
OL,3,CRising fuel bills hit lifesaving blood
OL,4,Cbiker service
OL,6,FDavid Hook, from Dumfries and Galloway
OL,7,FBlood Bike, said: "It's hurting the
OL,8,Fcharity really bad at the moment.
OL,10,F"Over the year, it means we need to
OL,11,Ffind another #18,000 just to cover the
OL,12,Fadditional fuel costs.
OL,14,F"The fundraisers play a major part,
OL,15,Fbecause without the money we couldn't
OL,16,Foperate. We don't take any funding
OL,17,Ffrom the NHS."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
