OL,3,CRising fuel bills hit lifesaving blood
OL,4,Cbiker service
OL,6,FIt is the only blood bike team in
OL,7,FScotland which runs 24 hours, seven
OL,8,Fdays a week. The group hope more
OL,9,Fpeople will get involved.
OL,11,FMarion Harris, from the charity, said:
OL,12,F"In order for us to keep going and our
OL,13,Fwheels turning it is the fundraising
OL,14,Fand the events that we do cover, and
OL,15,Fwe really do need to be out once a
OL,16,Fweek in the summer time because that
OL,17,Fis our biggest part of donations
OL,18,Fcoming in.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
